        },
        {
          "id": "market-security-mode",
          "label": "Market Security Mode",
          "type": "box",
          "shapeId": "entity",
          "semanticTypeId": "market-entity",
          "description": "A per-security toggle on a Market Account that enables or disables trading of a specific instrument. Keyed by market_id (→ AVA markets) and security_id (→ AVA securities) — cross-DB implicit FKs, not SQL-enforced. Both the security mode and Market Data feed must be active for a Hedge Order to proceed.",
